<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٣٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6106">مُسْلِمُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6685">هِشَامٌ </a>قَالَ: كَتَبَ إِلَيَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6882">يَحْيَى </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3554">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ أَبِي قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1219">أَبِيهِ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٣٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5"><span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">«إِذَا أُقِيمَتِ الصَّلَاةُ فَلَا تَقُومُوا حَتَّى تَرَوْنِي»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>